#' @title Col rename
#' @description Renames a source column to a target column
#' @type derivation
#' @param self Character string. The name of the dataset being modified.
#' @param rename_var_upper Character string. The new column name after rename.
#' @param source_var_upper Character string. The existing column to be renamed.
#' @code
{{self}} <- {{self}} |> dplyr::rename({{rename_var_upper}} = {{source_var_upper}})
